Translated Text: I am sorry to have been missing. It wasn't my intention. I wanted to upload a video, I really wanted to upload a video, but I am in a new city and wanted to explore it. Not only that, I'm also adapting to a new culture and a new schedule. And well, editing was lazy, with which I continued procrastinating and procrastinating and did not upload any video for two weeks. Sorry from the heart I cannot promise that this occurrence will not happen again, but I will try not to happen.
